---
import CtaBlock from './CtaBlock.astro';
---
<section class="section bg-white">
  <div class="section-wide">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-center mb-12">
      How Does The <span class="text-pth-blue">Part-Time Hypnotist</span> Model Work?
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
      <div>
        <img src="/images/30-proof-comparison-table.png" alt="Most Coaches vs Part-Time Hypnotists comparison" class="rounded-xl shadow-2xl w-full" />
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-slate-700 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p>If you're struggling to close clients or keep them on long term and you know there must be a better way to run your coaching business — then you're right.</p>
        <p><strong class="text-slate-900">PTH™</strong> is designed to be a more profitable, time-efficient coaching business — one that is well-paid, delivers real transformation, and gives you plenty of free time to walk the dog.</p>
        <p>As opposed to the traditional coaching model which relies on one-off sessions, constant posting on social media, and selling your time for an hourly rate.</p>
        <p>PTH™ is a counterintuitive approach that helps you sell larger packages to clients <em>without any pushy selling</em> because they can feel the changes from the get-go.</p>
        <p>You deliver real results from the very first session while showing them just how much more is possible — instead of clients waiting three months to notice a shift.</p>
        <p class="text-pth-blue font-semibold">This is how we're able to earn $3-5k per month working with only a few clients every week, while other coaches are stuck grinding it out just to survive.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section bg-gradient-to-b from-pth-blue to-pth-blue-dark text-white">
  <div class="section-wide">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-center mb-10">
      Why Is <span class="text-pth-orange">NOW</span> The Best Time Ever<br />To Become A Hypnotist?
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-start">
      <div class="space-y-4 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p>The demand for what you're about to discover has never been higher.</p>
        <p>Anxiety rates are at an all-time high. Millions are struggling with weight loss, productivity, smoking cessation, phobias, and unresolved trauma. The world feels like it's getting worse and worse… and people are desperately searching for real solutions that actually work.</p>
        <p>That's good news if you're a hypnotist — because it means there's virtually an unlimited supply of people who need your help creating lasting change.</p>
        <p>But hypnosis isn't just for people who are really struggling. I used to work primarily with high performers — executives, entrepreneurs, athletes — who wanted to perform even better. CEOs who wanted to eliminate procrastination. Business owners who wanted to quit their 20-year smoking habit. Peak performers who wanted to overcome a specific fear holding them back.</p>
        <p>The Truth is that <strong>95-99% of people could benefit from these tools</strong>. Almost everyone is carrying around limiting beliefs, unresolved emotions, or behavioral patterns they'd love to change.</p>
        <p>And here's the kicker: while everyone else is panicking about AI replacing coaches and therapists, you'll be positioned as the premium <strong>human solution</strong> that AI can never replicate. You'll leverage AI tools to 10x your marketing and operations… while selling clients on the deep subconscious transformations that only human connection can deliver.</p>
        <p>The only people who need to worry about AI are the ones who don't know how to use it.</p>
        <p class="text-pth-orange font-semibold text-xl">Human connection has never been at more of a premium. You only need 5 clients per month to hit $5,000 in part-time income.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="md:sticky md:top-8">
        <img src="/images/31-proof-market-potential.png" alt="Market potential infographic" class="rounded-xl shadow-2xl w-full" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white text-slate-900 rounded-xl shadow-xl p-6 md:p-8">
      <img src="/images/32-about-host-stage-photo.jpg" alt="Dan Candell teaching live" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full md:max-w-md mx-auto mb-6" />
      <p class="text-center italic text-slate-700">
        Dan Candell teaching live audiences how to deliver rapid hypnotic transformations.
      </p>
    </div>
    <CtaBlock variant="solid" />
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section bg-slate-50">
  <div class="section-narrow">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-center mb-8">
      Does The Part-Time Hypnotist Work<br /><span class="text-pth-blue">Even If I'm Brand New?</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="space-y-4 text-base md:text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
      <p>This is the most commonly asked question by aspiring hypnotists before they start.</p>
      <p>The Part-Time Hypnotist system is specifically designed to work whether you're a complete beginner or already have experience in coaching, therapy, or healing work.</p>
      <p class="font-semibold">Here's how it works for both:</p>
      <p><strong>If you're already seeing clients</strong> in any capacity (coaching, therapy, massage, Reiki, etc.), you'll be able to use these hypnosis techniques immediately and bolt them onto your existing practice.</p>
      <p>Many of my mentees started seeing paying clients within a few weeks because they already had access to people who needed help.</p>
      <p><strong>If you've never worked with clients before</strong>, you'll start by using these tools on yourself first. Then you'll practice on willing friends and family members and witness the transformations unfold before your very eyes. Once you've successfully helped 2-3 people transform (even if it's just your spouse or best friend), you'll have more confidence and testimonials and could start charging money for your services.</p>
      <p>With more practice and experience, you'll get better and better at delivering transformations. But don't expect to heal years of generational trauma in two days.</p>
      <p>These are proven tools to get you started. Mastery comes with time and repetition — which is exactly what we cover in depth in the Part-Time Hypnosis Certification program for those who want to go deeper.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
